Package: tiDML
Title: Double Machine Learning with Tidymodels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
        c(person(given = "Justin", family = "Beresford",
             email = "justin.beresford@frontier-economics.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: TImplements Double Machine Learning (DML) with cross-fitting in the
    tidymodels ecosystem. Provides model-agnostic nuisance learners via parsnip
    and recipes, and a concise API for partially linear regression and related
    estimators. Methods follow recent literature on debiased machine learning.
